    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.收音室介紹<br>2.控制室介紹<br>3.收音室的音訊信號工作配置<br>4.控制室中的音訊信號工作配置<br>5.基本音訊工程概念簡介<br>6.音源的定義<br>7.麥克風簡介<br>8.錄音設備和音訊連接介紹<br>9.數位控台簡介<br>10.EQ和壓縮限制器簡介<br>11.Plug-in效果簡介<br>12.分組實作",
        "en": "1.Introduction to “Booth”<br>2.Introduction to “Control Room”<br>3.Audio Signals working routes in “Booth”<br>4.Audio Signals working routes in “Control Room”<br>5.Introduction to the Concept of Basic Audio Engineering<br>6.Definition of “Sound Source”<br>7.Introduction to Microphones<br>8.Introduction to Recording Facilities and the Audio Connection<br>9.Introduction to Digital Console<br>10.Introduction to Equalizer and Compressor/Limiter<br>11.Introduction to Plug-in Effects<br>12.Group Work"
